## v0.4.0

- Improved test performace: Reduces test load by 99% by using only Service resources for load generation.
- Improved test speed: Reducing deployment speed by deploying 10 services at a time.
- Added no_predict option: No prediction of resource usage, only output of measured values.
- Improved metrics accuracy of CPU and traffic: Fixed to get steady state metrics by increasing the wait time to avoid spikes.
- Improved templates resolution: Enable to specify Deployment and Service templates in CLI option.
- Improved CLI commands: reviewing names and descriptions.
- Improved log messages: Info level (--verbose 3) outputs the summary of the process, and Debug level (--verbose 4) outputs processing data.
- Improved maintainancebility: Renewal of the internal architecture.